## Limitations

This report is based on data and analyses available up to October 2023. The rapidly changing nature of the automotive market, influenced by ongoing supply chain issues and economic conditions, means that future trends may differ from current predictions. Additionally, regional variations in market conditions were not extensively covered, which may affect the applicability of these findings in different geographic areas.

